                            <comment id="12790959" author="dkulp" created="Tue, 15 Dec 2009 21:18:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Marking this invalid.  Per JAXB spec, the schemaLocation is required so not accepting it is OK.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12796322" author="dkulp" created="Mon, 4 Jan 2010 19:45:50 +0000"  >

&lt;p&gt;Kind of a regression as this feature was specifically added for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-1094&quot; title=&quot;Tooling binding file wsdllcaotion and schemaLocation improvement&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CXF-1094&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CXF-1094&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Semi-easy to add back in, but with a small performance penalty, but the penalty is really just hit for binding files with no schemaLocation so not a big deal for most use cases.  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
